snippet.title: Amber Heard never told Police Johnny Depp assaulted her with iPhone and claimed they had just argued
snippet.description:
Amber Heard never told Police Johnny Depp assaulted her with iPhone and claimed they had just argued

info

Amber Heard never told police Johnny Depp threw an iPhone at her face when they were called to the couple's Beverly Hills home last Saturday, and only mentioned an argument with her husband.

The actress claims to have been injured by Depp during the incident and produced images of the alleged attack as part of her request for a temporary restraining order, which was granted on Friday last week.

The 30-year-old was at the hearing and sported bruising around her right eye and cheek, allegedly caused by the mobile phone being thrown at her face.
